# Runfast: Saúde, Treino e Performance


![Status do Projeto](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-em%20desenvolvimento-yellow?style=for-the-badge)
###
![Tamanho do Repositório](https://img.shields.io/github/repo-size/Vogi-png/runfast-app?style=for-the-badge)
![Linguagens Utilizadas](https://img.shields.io/github/languages/count/Vogi-png/runfast-app?style=for-the-badge)
